settings.content: I received bouquets from them, and it’s my go to place for all my niece’s performances. The quality of the flowers is great they last a long time. And the creativity of the bouquets is wonderful. I’m so grateful they do what they do for me. Great job!
settings.title: Francisco Lachowski

settings.content: Sent flowers same day(Saturday) to my Aunt for her Birthday! Great service, delivery, price and product! My Aunt called me 3 days later to tell me the flowers look more beautiful today then when they were first delivered! Quality of flowers are amazing! Will be using you for all my flower needs!
settings.title: Gigi Hadid

settings.content: I love the flowers heather did for my wedding, absolutely gorgeous! The memorial planter for my dad was another beautiful piece of work done by heather. The flowers are so bright and beautiful and heather is the most pleasant and helpful person I know. I will be going back for all my flower needs.
settings.title: Sean O'Pry

settings.content: After looking at reviews on the knot I came across Gecko’s flower shop and they thankfully able to accommodate my order. Being out of state they were so awesome to work with me over the phone/ email, and they did an amazing job incorporating baseball roses in my bouquets and corsages. These ladies really knocked it out of the park!
